‚Ä¢	With Arabic, Spanish, Sanskrit, and Farsi, you‚Äôll notice semantic clustering‚Äîsame root systems across traditions (e.g. ÿ¨ÿ∞ÿ± in Arabic and dhƒÅtu in Sanskrit).
